    <stitle>FRONT DRIVE AXLE WHEEL ENDS: FABCO SDA-12 - REASSEMBLY - UNIVERSAL JOINT ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="assemble" graphiccount="0">
        <title>UNIVERSAL JOINT ASSEMBLY</title>
        <para>Install the universal joint cross and bearing assembly with two bolts in each of the bearing caps. Refer
            to
            <hotlnk document="s02010_20.xml" xrefid="f0201029">Figure 29</hotlnk>
            and
            <hotlnk document="s02010_12.xml" xrefid="f0201021">Figure 21</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <para>Rotate the wheel hub to rotate the universal joint while the end is turned against the steering stop and
            check for positive clearance. Refer to
            <hotlnk document="s02010_5.xml" xrefid="hl0201008">ADJUSTMENTS, STEERING STOP</hotlnk>
            and
            <hotlnk document="s02010_5.xml" xrefid="f0201008">Figure 8</hotlnk>,
            <hotlnk document="s02010_5.xml" xrefid="f0201009">Figure 9</hotlnk>
            and
            <hotlnk document="s02010_5.xml" xrefid="f0201010">Figure 10</hotlnk>.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
